title: Deity of Miracle Vegan Resto
typeOfFood: Vegan, Chinese, Juice bar, Balinese, Indonesian
description: Vegan restaurant located to the left of Rofa Galleria Hotel. Serves many varieties of mock meats, plus vegetable, salad, rice, noodle, desserts, and a juice bar. Prior to March 2013 was at Jl. Sunset Road 88, Kuta.
